{"tid":1423000,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"＜支持警察＞當香港公安check你身分證時，主動關心吓佢","createTime":"2019-08-06T12:35:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T13:30:49.000Z","uid":90413,"like":4,"dislike":73,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"52745c4c033b3553d51725bc169cbe41f9ad7f7a","tid":1423000,"uid":90413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T12:35:45.000Z","msg":"我朋友相當支持警方執法，呢個兩個月佢地好辛苦又要打人，又要諗OT錢點洗，<br />\n所以大家要跟足以下方法關心警犬呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港公安為人民服務，辛苦了。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以下場景為俾香港公安check身分證時：<br />\n<br />\nPoint 1: <br />\n香港公安：先生，請出示身分證。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n自己：（喺附近揾香港市民幫忙拍片影低，最好嗰個市民企喺自己左右後少少，可以影低公安正面/冇人就自己嚟或者唔拍。）<br />\n*盡量唔好影到自己同其他香港人，可能佢哋為人低調唔想俾人影<br />\n<br />\n啊sir，我想睇吓委任證（警察通例）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nPoint 2: <br />\n香港公安：先生，麻煩俾個袋我哋檢查吓 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n自己：啊sir，當然冇問題啦。我唔似嗰啲冇血性嘅人渣咁，攞住碌棍去地鐵站打人。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如香港公安唔答/敷衍，完。<br />\n<br />\n如香港公安講任何嘢覺得你話緊佢，你可以講：啊sir，我講緊元朗嗰班白衣人喎，盧偉聰同林病，啊唔係，係林鄭，都話要嚴懲佢哋喎，啊sir你咁激動做咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nPoint 3:<br />\n自己：啊sir，我覺得啲警犬好型呀，有冇方法可以同佢哋合照？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如香港公安唔答/敷衍，完。<br />\n<br />\n如香港公安講任何嘢覺得你話緊佢，你可以講：啊sir，警犬喎，狗喎，即係獅子狗嗰啲喎。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如香港公安講任何嘢覺得你話緊佢，你可以講：啊sir，我講緊獅子狗喎，即係北京狗喎，我讀得書少啫，我識google維基㗎喎，唔信你自己上網睇吓。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nPoint 4: 視天氣而定<br />\n<br />\n當香港公安準備走，你可以講<br />\n<br />\n晴天<br />\n啊sir，今日好熱呀，小心中暑呀。頂唔順就入商場嘆吓冷氣啦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n陰天/落雨<br />\n啊sir，落雨嗰陣記得揾個商場避吓雨呀。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n作為一個有良心嘅香港人，當然要關心吓香港公安啦<br />\n<br />\n不過當然要睇人數啦，如果狗狗太多咁大家就要做李小龍啦<br />\n如果唔係狗狗會好惡發癲咬人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但如果大家身邊多同路人既咁就要盡情關心警察叔叔啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b322eaf02c161a68b3607bedde6c662ff064bf9","tid":1423000,"uid":74028,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T12:39:12.000Z","msg":"UP咩9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f90c242c706a1364d0ac19e0eeb5068a682d200","tid":1423000,"uid":34383,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T12:42:15.000Z","msg":"條條大路通羅馬"},{"pid":"0937bed2835cd9e285174c7ce7dc9fca8a196821","tid":1423000,"uid":145558,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T12:43:29.000Z","msg":"好尷尬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56f689cc028fa6cd67e20c50fb2c52dcac011c2a","tid":1423000,"uid":90413,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"4b322eaf02c161a68b3607bedde6c662ff064bf9","tid":1423000,"uid":74028,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T12:39:12.000Z","msg":"UP咩9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T12:45:30.000Z","msg":"你係咪黃絲？"},{"pid":"92e9c310ef6bd604cde49990706ca628a0abd806","